snippet.title: The Coma 2B: Catacomb - Official Debut Trailer
snippet.description: The Coma 2B: Catacomb is a Korean survival horror-adventure. It is a back story of the previous game The Coma 2: Vicious Sisters, and a story bridge of all series. You are back in game as Youngho Choi, the main protagonist of The Coma 1, you must venture from the mirror dimension of reality to survive. What happened between The Coma 1 and The Coma 2? The answer is in here.
